nodes.name: 5-Formyltetrahydrofolate cyclo-ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + Folinic acid + H+ <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + 5,10-Methenyltetrahydrofolate

nodes.name: 10-formyltetrahydrofolate:NADP+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: 10-Formyltetrahydrofolate + NADP+ + H2O <=> Tetrahydrofolate + CO2 + NADPH + H+

nodes.name: 5,10-methylenetetrahydrofolate,NADPH:dUMP C-methyltransferase
nodes.rxn: 5,10-Methylenetetrahydrofolate + dUMP + NADPH + H+ <=> Tetrahydrofolate + dTMP + NADP+
